---
description: Code, docs and comments in the project must be in English
alwaysApply: true
---

# Language: English in the codebase

- **Code**: Variable names, function names, strings in code, and file content produced for the project must be in **English**.
- **Documentation**: README, MDX/Storybook docs, ANALYSE.md, and any other project docs must be in **English**.
- **Comments**: In-code comments (JS/TS/CSS/config) must be in **English**.

This applies only to what is written in the repository. The assistant may reply to the user in the user's language (e.g. French).
